<b data-is-speakable="">Get This: Warming Planet Can Mean More Snow</b> <b data-is-speakable="">With snow blanketing much of the country, the topic of global warming has become the butt of jokes. But most scientists who study the climate don't see a contradiction between a warming world and lots of snow.</b>
